#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_progress.py:164
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%s is now successfully installed and ready for you to use!\n"
"Go ahead and quit the application to start using it!"
msgstr ""
"ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %s ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ແລະ ພ້ອມໃຫ້ທ່ານນຳໃຊ້!\n"
"ກະລຸນາອອກຈາກແອັບພລິເຄຊັນເພື່ອເລີ່ມການນຳໃຊ້!"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_progress.py:159
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%s is now successfully installed and ready for you to use!\n"
"Go ahead and reboot your system to start using it!"
msgstr ""
"ການຕິດຕັ້ງ %s ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ແລະ ພ້ອມໃຫ້ທ່ານນຳໃຊ້!\n"
"ກະລຸນາປິດເປີດລະບົບຂອງທ່ານໃໝ່ເພື່ອເລີ່ມການນຳໃຊ້!"

