#: pyanaconda/display.py:324
msgid ""
"Text mode provides a limited set of installation options. It does not offer "
"custom partitioning for full control over the disk layout. Would you like to "
"use VNC mode instead?"
msgstr ""
"ໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມມີຕົວເລືອກການຕິດຕັ້ງທີ່ຈຳກັດ. "
"ມັນບໍ່ມີການແບ່ງພາທິຊັນແບບກຳນົດເອງເພື່ອຄວບຄຸມຮູບແບບດິສຢ່າງເຕັມສ່ວນ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ໂໝດ VNC ແທນບໍ່?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/custom_storage_helpers.glade:460
