msgstr "ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບປະເພດລະບົບໄຟລ໌ \"%s\"."

#: pyanaconda/kickstart.py:315
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The %%anaconda section has been deprecated. It may be removed from future "
"releases, which will result in a fatal error when it is encountered. Please "
"modify your kickstart file to remove this section."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນ %%anaconda ຖືກຍົກເລີກການນຳໃຊ້ແລ້ວ. ມັນອາດຈະຖືກຖອນອອກໃນເວີຊັນໃນອະນາຄົດ, "
"ເຊິ່ງຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຮ້າຍແຮງເມື່ອພົບເຫັນ. ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ kickstart "
"ຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອຖອນສ່ວນນີ້ອອກ."

#: pyanaconda/startup_utils.py:100
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The %(product_name)s graphical installer requires %(needed_ram)s MB of "
"memory, but you only have %(total_ram)s MB.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງແບບກຣາຟິກ %(product_name)s ຕ້ອງການໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(needed_ram)s MB, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງ "
"%(total_ram)s MB.\n"

#: pyanaconda/modules/payloads/kickstart.py:44
msgid "The %packages --ignorebroken feature is not supported on your product!"
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດ %packages --ignorebroken ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບໃນຜະລິດຕະພັນຂອງທ່ານ!"

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:114
msgid ""
"The 'boot' area on your computer is where files needed\n"
"to start the operating system are stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'boot' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນເກັບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຈຳເປັນ\n"
"ໃນການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນລະບົບປະຕິບັດການ."

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:118
msgid ""
"The 'home' area on your computer is where all your personal\n"
"data is stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'home' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນທີ່ເກັບຂໍ້ມູນ\n"
"ສ່ວນຕົວຂອງທ່ານທັງໝົດ."

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:116
msgid ""
"The 'root' area on your computer is where core system\n"
"files and applications are stored."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'root' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນບ່ອນເກັບໄຟລ໌ລະບົບຫຼັກ\n"
"ແລະ ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນຕ່າງໆ."

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:112
msgid ""
"The 'swap' area on your computer is used by the operating\n"
"system when running low on memory."
msgstr ""
"ພື້ນທີ່ 'swap' ໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານຖືກໃຊ້ໂດຍລະບົບ\n"
"ປະຕິບັດການເມື່ອໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳເຫຼືອໜ້ອຍ."

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:120
msgid ""
"The BIOS boot partition is required to enable booting\n"
"from GPT-partitioned disks on BIOS hardware."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີພາຕິຊັນ BIOS boot ເພື່ອເປີດການບູດ\n"
"ຈາກດິສກ໌ທີ່ແບ່ງແບບ GPT ໃນຮາດແວ BIOS."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:94
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The LDL DASD disk {name} ({busid}) cannot be used for the installation. "
"Please format it."
msgstr "ດິສກ໌ LDL DASD {name} ({busid}) ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງໄດ້. ກະລຸນາຟໍແມັດມັນກ່ອນ."

#: pyanaconda/core/storage.py:122
msgid ""
"The PReP boot partition is required as part of the\n"
"boot loader configuration on some PPC platforms."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີພາຕິຊັນ PReP boot ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງ\n"
"ການຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວໂຫຼດບູດໃນບາງແພລັດຟອມ PPC."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:365
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The RAID level you have selected ({level}) requires more disks ({min}) than "
"you currently have selected ({count})."
msgstr ""
"ລະດັບ RAID ທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກ ({level}) ຕ້ອງການດິດ ({min}) ຫຼາຍກວ່າທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ "
"({count})."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:660
#, python-format
msgid "The RAID volume name \"%s\" is already in use."
msgstr "ຊື່ວໍລຸມ RAID \"%s\" ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/vnc.py:258
msgid "The VNC server is now running."
msgstr "ເຊີບເວີ VNC ກຳລັງເຮັດວຽກຢູ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/dasd.glade:324
msgid "The added DASD can be found under \"Local Standard Disks.\""
msgstr "DASD ທີ່ເພີ່ມສາມາດພົບໄດ້ພາຍໃຕ້ \"Local Standard Disks.\""

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:465
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The available memory is less than %(size)s which can be too small for LUKS2 "
"format. It may fail."
msgstr ""
"ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳທີ່ມີຢູ່ແມ່ນໜ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງອາດຈະໜ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບຮູບແບບ LUKS2. ມັນອາດຈະຫຼົ້ມເຫຼວ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/custom_storage.py:871
msgid "The container is encrypted."
msgstr "ຄອນເທນເນີຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:422
msgid ""
"The existing unlocked LUKS device {} cannot be used for the installation "
"without an encryption key specified for this device. Please, rescan the "
"storage."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນ LUKS {} ທີ່ປົດລັອກຢູ່ແລ້ວ ບໍ່ສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໃນການຕິດຕັ້ງໄດ້ "
"ໂດຍທີ່ບໍ່ມີການລະບຸລະຫັດການເຂົ້າລະຫັດສຳລັບອຸປະກອນນີ້. ກະລຸນາສະແກນບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນຄືນໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/nvdimm.glade:70
msgid ""
"The following NVDIMM devices selected from the list will be reconfigured to "
"sector mode:"
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນ NVDIMM ຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ທີ່ເລືອກຈາກລາຍການຈະຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າໃໝ່ເປັນໂໝດເຊັກເຕີ:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/dasd.glade:227
msgid ""
"The following error occurred discovering DASD devices.  Please double check "
"your configuration information and try again."
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນການຄົ້ນຫາອຸປະກອນ DASD. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານອີກຄັ້ງແລະລອງໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/iscsi.glade:556
msgid ""
"The following error occurred discovering iSCSI targets.  Please double check "
"your authorization information and try again."
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນການຄົ້ນຫາເປົ້າໝາຍ iSCSI. "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນການອະນຸຍາດຂອງທ່ານອີກຄັ້ງແລະລອງໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/zfcp.glade:269
msgid ""
"The following error occurred discovering zFCP devices.  Please double check "
"your configuration information and try again."
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນການຄົ້ນຫາອຸປະກອນ zFCP.  ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານອີກຄັ້ງແລະລອງໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/errors.py:238
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The following error occurred during the installation:\n"
"\n"
"{details}\n"
"\n"
"Would you like to ignore this and continue with installation?"
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນລະຫວ່າງການຕິດຕັ້ງ:\n"
"\n"
"{details}\n"
"\n"
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຂ້າມຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້ ແລະ ສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງຫຼືບໍ່?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/iscsi.glade:1084
msgid ""
"The following error occurred logging into the selected iSCSI node.  Please "
"double check your authorization information and try again."
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບໂນດ iSCSI ທີ່ເລືອກ. "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ມູນການອະນຸຍາດຂອງທ່ານອີກຄັ້ງແລະລອງໃໝ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/nvdimm.glade:205
msgid "The following error occurred reconfiguring NVDIMM devices:"
msgstr "ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນການກຳນົດຄ່າອຸປະກອນ NVDIMM ໃໝ່:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/fcoe.glade:215
msgid ""
"The following error occurred while attempting to add an FCoE SAN.  Please "
"check your configuration and try again"
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ພະຍາຍາມເພີ່ມ FCoE SAN.  "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບການຕັ້ງຄ່າຂອງທ່ານແລະລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງ"

#: pyanaconda/errors.py:219
msgid ""
"The following error occurred while installing the boot loader. The system "
"will not be bootable. Would you like to ignore this and continue with "
"installation?"
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງ boot loader. ລະບົບຈະບໍ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້. "
