"The pwpolicy command has been deprecated. It may be removed from future "
"releases, which will result in a fatal error when it is encountered. Please "
"modify your kickstart file to remove this command."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງ pwpolicy ຖືກຍົກເລີກການນຳໃຊ້ແລ້ວ. ມັນອາດຈະຖືກຖອນອອກໃນເວີຊັນໃນອະນາຄົດ, "
"ເຊິ່ງຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຮ້າຍແຮງເມື່ອພົບເຫັນ. ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ kickstart "
"ຂອງທ່ານເພື່ອຖອນຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ອອກ."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:320
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The rescue environment will now attempt to find your Linux installation and "
"mount it under the directory : %s.  You can then make any changes required "
"to your system.  Choose '1' to proceed with this step.\n"
"You can choose to mount your file systems read-only instead of read-write by "
"choosing '2'.\n"
"If for some reason this process does not work choose '3' to skip directly to "
"a shell.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບກູ້ຄືນຈະພະຍາຍາມຊອກຫາການຕິດຕັ້ງ Linux ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ມັນໄວ້ພາຍໃຕ້ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ: %s. "
"ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງສິ່ງຕ່າງໆທີ່ຈຳເປັນຕໍ່ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ເລືອກ '1' "
"ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້.\n"
"ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະບົບໄຟລ໌ຂອງທ່ານແບບອ່ານຢ່າງດຽວ (read-only) ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນແບບອ່ານ-ຂຽນ "
"(read-write) ໂດຍການເລືອກ '2'.\n"
"ຫາກຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ໃຊ້ການບໍ່ໄດ້ຍ້ອນເຫດຜົນບາງຢ່າງ ໃຫ້ເລືອກ '3' ເພື່ອຂ້າມໄປໃຊ້ shell ໂດຍກົງ.\n"
"\n"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/root_password.glade:165
msgid ""
"The root account is used for administering the system.  Enter a password for "
"the root user."
msgstr "ບັນຊີ root ຖືກໃຊ້ສຳລັບການບໍລິຫານລະບົບ. ປ້ອນລະຫັດຜ່ານສຳລັບຜູ້ໃຊ້ root."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/disk_selection/utils.py:36
msgid "The selected disk {} is not recognized."
msgstr "ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກດິສກ໌ {} ທີ່ເລືອກ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:263
#, python-format
msgid "The size \"%s\" is invalid."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດ \"%s\" ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/software_selection.py:698
msgid ""
"The software marked for installation has the following errors.  This is "
"likely caused by an error with your installation source.  You can quit the "
"installer, change your software source, or change your software selections."
msgstr ""
"ຊອບແວທີ່ຖືກໝາຍໃຫ້ຕິດຕັ້ງມີຂໍ້ຜິດພາດດັ່ງຕໍ່ໄປນີ້. ນີ້ອາດເກີດຈາກຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຂອງແຫຼ່ງການຕິດຕັ້ງຂອງທ່ານ. "
"ທ່ານສາມາດອອກຈາກຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງ, ປ່ຽນແຫຼ່ງຊອບແວ, ຫຼື ປ່ຽນການເລືອກຊອບແວຂອງທ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/custom_storage.py:900
msgid ""
"The space available to this mount point can be changed by modifying the "
"volume below."
msgstr "ພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ໃຊ້ໄດ້ສຳລັບຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນີ້ ສາມາດປ່ຽນແປງໄດ້ໂດຍການແກ້ໄຂວໍລຸມດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/subscription.glade:796
msgid "The system is currently not registered."
msgstr "ປັດຈຸບັນລະບົບຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ລົງທະບຽນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/subscription.py:1124
msgid "The system is registered to a Satellite instance."
msgstr "ລະບົບໄດ້ຖືກລົງທະບຽນກັບ Satellite instance ແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/subscription.py:1128
msgid "The system is registered."
msgstr "ລະບົບໄດ້ຖືກລົງທະບຽນແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:830
#, python-format
msgid "The volume group name \"%s\" is already in use."
msgstr "ຊື່ກຸ່ມວໍລຸມ \"%s\" ຖືກນຳໃຊ້ແລ້ວ."

#: pyanaconda/errors.py:147
msgid ""
"There is a problem with your existing storage configuration or your initial "
"settings, for example a kickstart file. You must resolve this matter before "
"the installation can proceed. There is a shell available for use which you "
"can access by pressing ctrl-alt-f1 and then ctrl-b 2.\n"
"\n"
"Once you have resolved the issue you can retry the storage scan. If you do "
"not fix it you will have to exit the installer."
msgstr ""
"ມີບັນຫາກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼື ການຕັ້ງຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງທ່ານ, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ ໄຟລ໌ kickstart. "
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂບັນຫານີ້ກ່ອນການຕິດຕັ້ງຈະດຳເນີນຕໍ່ໄປໄດ້. ມີ shell "
"ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ໂດຍການກົດ ctrl-alt-f1 ແລະ ຈາກນັ້ນກົດ ctrl-b 2.\n"
"\n"
"ເມື່ອທ່ານແກ້ໄຂບັນຫາແລ້ວ ທ່ານສາມາດລອງສະແກນບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່. ຫາກທ່ານບໍ່ແກ້ໄຂ "
"ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງອອກຈາກຕົວຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/resize.py:161
msgid ""
"There is also free space available in pre-existing file systems.  While it's "
"risky and we recommend you back up your data first, you can recover that "
"free disk space and make it available for this installation below."
msgstr ""
"ມີພື້ນທີ່ຫວ່າງໃນລະບົບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່ກ່ອນແລ້ວ. ເຖິງວ່າມັນຈະມີຄວາມສ່ຽງ ແລະ "
"ພວກເຮົາແນະນຳໃຫ້ທ່ານສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ອນ, ທ່ານສາມາດກູ້ຄືນພື້ນທີ່ດິສກ໌ຫວ່າງນັ້ນ ແລະ "
"ນຳມາໃຊ້ສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງນີ້ຢູ່ດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/devicetree/fsset.py:435
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"There is an entry in your /etc/fstab file that contains an invalid or "
"incorrect file system type. The file says that {detected_type} at "
"{mount_point} is {fstab_type}."
msgstr ""
"ມີລາຍການໃນໄຟລ໌ /etc/fstab ຂອງທ່ານທີ່ມີປະເພດລະບົບໄຟລ໌ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໄຟລ໌ລະບຸວ່າ {detected_type} "
"ທີ່ {mount_point} ແມ່ນ {fstab_type}."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/storage.py:795
msgid "There was a problem with your disk selection. Click here for details."
msgstr "ມີບັນຫາກັບການເລືອກດິສກ໌ຂອງທ່ານ. ຄລິກທີ່ນີ້ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດ."

#: pyanaconda/errors.py:187
#, python-format
msgid ""
"There was an error running the kickstart script at line %(lineno)s.  This is "
"a fatal error and installation will be aborted.  The details of this error "
"are:\n"
"\n"
"%(details)s"
msgstr ""
"ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນການຣັນສະຄຣິບ kickstart ທີ່ແຖວ %(lineno)s. ນີ້ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຮ້າຍແຮງ ແລະ "
"ການຕິດຕັ້ງຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກ. ລາຍລະອຽດຂອງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້ຄື:\n"
"\n"
"%(details)s"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:1258
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This %(type)s device is missing member devices. You can remove it or select "
"a different device."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນ %(type)s ນີ້ຂາດຫາຍອຸປະກອນສະມາຊິກ. ທ່ານສາມາດລຶບມັນອອກ ຫຼື ເລືອກອຸປະກອນອື່ນ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:1254
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This LVM Volume Group is missing %(missingPVs)d of %(totalPVs)d physical "
"volumes. You can remove it or select a different device."
msgstr ""
"LVM Volume Group ນີ້ຂາດຫາຍໄປ %(missingPVs)d ຈາກທັງໝົດ %(totalPVs)d "
"ວໍລຸມທາງກາຍະພາບ. ທ່ານສາມາດລຶບມັນອອກ ຫຼື ເລືອກອຸປະກອນອື່ນ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:1247
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This Software RAID array is missing %(missing)d of %(total)d member "
"partitions. You can remove it or select a different device."
msgstr ""
"ອາເຣ Software RAID ນີ້ຂາດຫາຍໄປ %(missing)d ຈາກທັງໝົດ %(total)d ພາທິຊັນສະມາຊິກ. "
"ທ່ານສາມາດລຶບມັນອອກ ຫຼື ເລືອກອຸປະກອນອື່ນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/datetime_spoke.glade:212
msgid "This URL refers to a pool of NTP servers"
msgstr "URL ນີ້ອ້າງອີງເຖິງກຸ່ມຂອງເຊີບເວີ NTP"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/custom_storage.glade:1276
msgid ""
"This device cannot be edited directly. You can remove it or select a "
"different device."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນນີ້ບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໂດຍກົງໄດ້. ທ່ານສາມາດລຶບມັນອອກ ຫຼື ເລືອກອຸປະກອນອື່ນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/resize.py:135
msgid "This device contains the installation source."
msgstr "ອຸປະກອນນີ້ມີແຫຼ່ງການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/custom_storage.glade:1129
msgid ""
"This device is encrypted and cannot be read without a valid passphrase. You "
"may unlock it below."
msgstr ""
"ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຖືກເຂົ້າລະຫັດໄວ້ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ມີວະລີຜ່ານທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ທ່ານສາມາດປົດລັອກມັນໄດ້ຢູ່ດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_source.glade:982
#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_source.glade:983
msgid "This field is optional."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງນີ້ເປັນທາງເລືອກ (ບໍ່ບັງຄັບ)."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/custom_storage.py:905
msgid "This file system may not be resized."
msgstr "ລະບົບໄຟລ໌ນີ້ອາດຈະບໍ່ສາມາດປັບຂະໜາດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/core/constants.py:158
msgid ""
"This hardware (or a combination thereof) is not supported by Red Hat. For "
"more information on supported hardware, please refer to http://"
"www.redhat.com/hardware."
msgstr ""
"ຮາດແວນີ້ (ຫຼື ການປະສົມປະສານຂອງມັນ) ບໍ່ຖືກຮອງຮັບໂດຍ Red Hat. "
"ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບຮາດແວທີ່ຮອງຮັບ, ກະລຸນາອ້າງອີງເຖິງ http://www.redhat.com/hardware."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/beta_warning_dialog.glade:68
msgid "This is unstable, pre-release software."
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນຊອບແວທີ່ບໍ່ໝັ້ນຄົງ, ເປັນລຸ້ນກ່ອນການປ່ອຍ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/storage.py:365
msgid "This may take a moment."
msgstr "ອາດໃຊ້ເວລາຈັກໜ່ອຍ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/dasdfmt.glade:209
msgid ""
"This may take a moment. You may <a href=\"\">go back to the main menu</a> to "
"complete other installation options while formatting completes."
msgstr ""
"ອາດຈະໃຊ້ເວລາຈັກໜ່ອຍ. ທ່ານອາດຈະ <a href=\"\">ກັບໄປທີ່ເມນູຫຼັກ</a> "
"ເພື່ອເຮັດສຳເລັດຕົວເລືອກການຕິດຕັ້ງອື່ນໆໃນຂະນະທີ່ການຟໍແມັດກຳລັງດຳເນີນໄປ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_source.py:392
msgctxt "GUI|Software Source|Media Check Dialog"
msgid "This media is good to install from."
msgstr "ມີເດຍນີ້ດີພ້ອມສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_source.py:408
msgctxt "GUI|Software Source|Media Check Dialog"
msgid "This media is not good to install from."
msgstr "ມີເດຍນີ້ບໍ່ດີພ້ອມສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:364
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This mount point is invalid. The %s directory must be on the / file system."
msgstr "ຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ໄດເຣັກທໍຣີ %s ຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງ/ລະບົບໄຟລ໌."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/time_spoke.py:70
msgid "Time settings"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າເວລາ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/time_spoke.py:127
msgid "Timezone is not set."
msgstr "ເຂດເວລາຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/time_spoke.py:221
msgid "Timezone settings"
msgstr "ການຕັ້ງຄ່າເຂດເວລາ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/time_spoke.py:143
#, python-format
msgid "Timezone: %s\n"
msgstr "ເຂດເວລາ: %s\n"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advanced_user.glade:348
msgid "Tip:"
msgstr "ເຄັດລັບ:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/dasd.glade:90
msgid "To use DASD disks, you must provide the device number."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຊ້ດິດ DASD, ທ່ານຕ້ອງໃຫ້ໝາຍເລກອຸປະກອນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advstorage/iscsi.glade:114
msgid ""
"To use iSCSI disks, you must provide the address of your iSCSI target and "
"the iSCSI initiator name you've configured for your host."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຊ້ດິດ iSCSI, ທ່ານຕ້ອງໃຫ້ທີ່ຢູ່ຂອງເປົ້າໝາຍ iSCSI ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຊື່ຕົວເລີ່ມ iSCSI "
