msgstr ""
"X ບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມເຮັດວຽກໃນເຄື່ອງຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມ VNC "
"ເພື່ອເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຫາຄອມພິວເຕີເຄື່ອງນີ້ຈາກຄອມພິວເຕີເຄື່ອງອື່ນ ແລະ ດຳເນີນການຕິດຕັ້ງແບບກຣາຟິກ ຫຼື "
"ຈະຕິດຕັ້ງຕໍ່ດ້ວຍໂໝດຂໍ້ຄວາມ?"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/resize.py:154
msgid ""
"You can remove existing file systems you no longer need to free up space for "
"this installation.  Removing a file system will permanently delete all of "
"the data it contains."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດລຶບລະບົບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່ທີ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງການແລ້ວ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມພື້ນທີ່ຫວ່າງສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງນີ້. "
"ການລຶບລະບົບໄຟລ໌ຈະລຶບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດໃນນັ້ນຢ່າງຖາວອນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade:87
msgid ""
"You can remove or insert additional disks at this time and press 'Rescan "
"Disks' below for the changes to take effect."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຖອດ ຫຼື ໃສ່ດິດເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້ໃນເວລານີ້ ແລະ ກົດ 'ສະແກນດິດໃໝ່' ດ້ານລຸ່ມເພື່ອໃຫ້ການປ່ຽນແປງມີຜົນ."

#: pyanaconda/rescue.py:491
msgid "You don't have any Linux partitions.\n"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ມີພາທິຊັນ Linux ໃດໆ.\n"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/passphrase.glade:81
msgid ""
"You have chosen to encrypt some of your data. You will need to create a "
"passphrase that you will use to access your data when you start your "
"computer."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ເລືອກທີ່ຈະເຂົ້າລະຫັດຂໍ້ມູນບາງສ່ວນຂອງທ່ານ. "
"ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງສ້າງວະລີຜ່ານທີ່ທ່ານຈະໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຂົ້າເຖິງຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານເມື່ອທ່ານເປີດຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/storage.py:617
msgid ""
"You have chosen to skip boot loader installation. Your system may not be "
"bootable."
msgstr "ທ່ານໄດ້ເລືອກທີ່ຈະຂ້າມການຕິດຕັ້ງຕົວໂຫຼດບູດ. ລະບົບຂອງທ່ານອາດຈະບໍ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/datetime_spoke.py:1126
msgid "You have no working NTP server configured"
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຕັ້ງຄ່າເຊີບເວີ NTP ທີ່ໃຊ້ງານໄດ້"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:197
msgid "You have not created a bootable partition."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ສ້າງພາຕິຊັນທີ່ສາມາດບູດໄດ້."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:64
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not defined a root partition (/), which is required for "
"installation of %s to continue."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດພາຕິຊັນຮາກ (root) (/), ເຊິ່ງຈຳເປັນສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %s ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:314
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. %(requiredMem)s of memory is "
"recommended to continue installation without a swap partition, but you only "
"have %(installedMem)s."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ແນະນຳໃຫ້ມີໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(requiredMem)s "
"ເພື່ອສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງໂດຍບໍ່ມີພາຕິຊັນ swap, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(installedMem)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:321
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. %(requiredMem)s of memory is "
"required to continue installation without a swap partition, but you only "
"have %(installedMem)s."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງມີໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳ %(requiredMem)s "
"ເພື່ອສືບຕໍ່ການຕິດຕັ້ງໂດຍບໍ່ມີພາຕິຊັນ swap, ແຕ່ທ່ານມີພຽງແຕ່ %(installedMem)s."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:327
msgid ""
"You have not specified a swap partition. Although not strictly required in "
"all cases, it will significantly improve performance for most installations."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸພາຕິຊັນ swap. ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າມັນຈະບໍ່ໄດ້ບັງຄັບໃນທຸກກໍລະນີ, "
"ແຕ່ມັນຈະປັບປຸງປະສິດທິພາບຢ່າງຫຼວງຫຼາຍສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງສ່ວນໃຫຍ່."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/accordion.py:470
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You haven't created any mount points for your %(product)s %(version)s "
"installation yet.  You can:"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ສ້າງຈຸດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ (mount point) ໃດໆສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ %(product)s %(version)s "
"ຂອງທ່ານເທື່ອ. ທ່ານສາມາດ:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/refresh.glade:223
msgid ""
"You may <a href=\"\">go back to the main menu</a> to complete other\n"
"installation options while this scan completes."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານອາດຈະ <a href=\"\">ກັບໄປທີ່ເມນູຫຼັກ</a> ເພື່ອເຮັດສຳເລັດຕົວເລືອກ\n"
"ການຕິດຕັ້ງອື່ນໆໃນຂະນະທີ່ການສະແກນນີ້ກຳລັງດຳເນີນໄປ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/keyboard.glade:482
msgid "You may add a keyboard layout by selecting it below:"
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມຮູບແບບແປ້ນພິມໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກມັນດ້ານລຸ່ມ:"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/advanced_user.glade:367
msgid ""
"You may input a comma-separated list of group names and group IDs here. "
"Groups that do not already exist will be created; specify their GID in "
"parentheses. "
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນລາຍຊື່ຊື່ກຸ່ມ ແລະ ID ກຸ່ມທີ່ຂັ້ນດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈຸດຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້. ກຸ່ມທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ມີຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ; ລະບຸ GID "
"ຂອງພວກມັນໃນວົງເລັບ. "

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:69
#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/interactive/utils.py:439
msgid "You must create a new file system on the root device."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງສ້າງລະບົບໄຟລ໌ໃໝ່ເທິງອຸປະກອນຮາກ (root)."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:315
msgid ""
"You must include a PReP Boot Partition within the first 4GiB of an MBR- or "
"GPT-formatted disk."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາພາທິຊັນບູດ PReP ພາຍໃນ 4GiB ທຳອິດຂອງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື GPT."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:354
msgid ""
"You must include an Apple Bootstrap Partition on an Apple Partition Map-"
"formatted disk."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາພາທິຊັນ Apple Bootstrap ເທິງດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ Apple Partition Map."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:404
msgid ""
"You must include at least one MBR- or DASD-formatted disk as an install "
"target."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື DASD ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:154
msgid ""
"You must include at least one MBR- or GPT-formatted disk as an install "
"target."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຫຼື GPT ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:442
msgid "You must include at least one MBR-formatted disk as an install target."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສທີ່ຟໍແມັດແບບ MBR ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:80
#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/platform.py:386
msgid "You must include at least one disk as an install target."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງລວມເອົາດິສຢ່າງໜ້ອຍໜຶ່ງໜ່ວຍເປັນເປົ້າໝາຍການຕິດຕັ້ງ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/tui/spokes/user.py:248
msgid "You must set a password"
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງຕັ້ງລະຫັດຜ່ານ"

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/installation_source.py:1204
msgid "You need to configure the network to use a network installation source."
msgstr "ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າເຄືອຂ່າຍເພື່ອໃຊ້ແຫຼ່ງການຕິດຕັ້ງຜ່ານເຄືອຂ່າຍ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/datetime_spoke.py:1122
msgid "You need to set up networking first if you want to use NTP"
msgstr "ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າເຄືອຂ່າຍກ່ອນ ຖ້າຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ NTP"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/disk_selection/utils.py:46
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You selected disk %(selected)s, which contains devices that also use "
"unselected disk %(unselected)s. You must select or de-select these disks as "
"a set."
msgid_plural ""
"You selected disk %(selected)s, which contains devices that also use "
"unselected disks %(unselected)s. You must select or de-select these disks as "
"a set."
msgstr[0] ""
"ທ່ານເລືອກດິສກ໌ %(selected)s ເຊິ່ງມີອຸປະກອນທີ່ນຳໃຊ້ດິສກ໌ %(unselected)s ທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເລືອກນຳ. "
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງເລືອກ ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກການເລືອກດິສກ໌ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເປັນຊຸດ."

#: pyanaconda/core/constants.py:231
msgid "You will have to press <b>Done</b> twice to confirm it."
msgstr "ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງກົດ <b>ສຳເລັດ</b> ສອງຄັ້ງເພື່ອຢືນຢັນມັນ."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/storage.glade:511
msgid "You'll set a passphrase next."
msgstr "ທ່ານຈະຕັ້ງວະລີຜ່ານໃນຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:132
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is less than %(size)s which is lower than "
"recommended for a normal %(productName)s install."
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍກວ່າ %(size)s ເຊິ່ງຕ່ຳກວ່າຂະໜາດທີ່ແນະນຳສຳລັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ "
"%(productName)s ປົກກະຕິ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:166
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too large for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ "
"%(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:160
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(mount)s partition is too small for %(format)s formatting (allowable "
"size is %(minSize)s to %(maxSize)s)"
msgstr ""
"ພາຕິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານນ້ອຍເກີນໄປສຳລັບການຟໍແມັດ %(format)s (ຂະໜາດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ "
"%(minSize)s ຫາ %(maxSize)s)"

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:140
#, python-format
msgid "Your %(mount)s partition size is lower than required %(size)s."
msgstr "ຂະໜາດພາທິຊັນ %(mount)s ຂອງທ່ານຕ່ຳກວ່າ %(size)s ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:380
#, python-format
msgid "Your %s must be on a separate partition or LV."
msgstr "%s ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງຢູ່ເທິງພາທິຊັນ ຫຼື LV ທີ່ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/checker/utils.py:232
msgid ""
"Your BIOS-based system needs a special partition to boot from a GPT disk "
"label. To continue, please create a 1MiB 'biosboot' type partition."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບທີ່ອີງໃສ່ BIOS ຂອງທ່ານຕ້ອງການພາຕິຊັນພິເສດເພື່ອບູດຈາກປ້າຍຊື່ດິສກ໌ GPT. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່, "
"ກະລຸນາສ້າງພາຕິຊັນປະເພດ 'biosboot' ຂະໜາດ 1MiB."

#: pyanaconda/ui/gui/spokes/lib/storage_dialogs.py:81
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your current <a href=\"\" title=\"%(tooltip)s\"><b>%(product)s</b> software "
"selection</a> requires <b>%(total)s</b> of available space, including "
"<b>%(software)s</b> for software and <b>%(swap)s</b> for swap space."
